title: I have not gotten my Starguardian Icon, yet :(
body:
I have not gotten my Starguardian Icon, yet :(

My sister MasterRage has not gotten it eather.

Why?

replies.body: The Mark of the Star Guardian account needs to process and unlock on the account, which may take a few days.  As long as you were signed in while taking the quiz, you'll be fine.  Hang tight!
It took me 4 days to get mine after I took the quiz! When did you take it?
Took it like when Jinx came out.
